x_1,...,x_k \in \Bbb N
c_1,...,c_k \in \Bbb N 
\sum_{j=1}^k c_j x_j
\operatorname{lcm}(x_1,...,x_k)
0 \leq d_j \leq c_j
\sum_{j=1}^k d_j x_j =\operatorname{lcm}(x_1,...,x_k)
\{3,4,15,24,30,40,60\}
3+4+15+2\times24+30+2\times40+60=2\times120
3a+4b+15c+24d+30e+40f+60g=120
a,b,\dots,g
a=b=c=1
d=2
30e+40f+60g=50
\{1,6,10,15\}
1+4\times6+2\times10+15=2\times30
